<i>noun</i>: 폭탄 [폭탄], 날벼락 [날벼락] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>폭탄 [폭탄]</dt><br>
<dd>bomb; bombshell</dd><br>
<dd>사람을 죽이거나 건물과 시설을 파괴하기 위해 던지거나 쏘거나 떨어뜨려서 터뜨리는 폭발물.</dd><br>
<dd>An explosive which explodes. when it is thrown, fired, or dropped, to kill people or destroy buildings and facilities.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>날벼락 [날벼락]</dt><br>
<dd>1. unexpected lightening</dd><br>
<dd>맑은 날씨에 갑자기 치는 벼락.</dd><br>
<dd>Thunderbolt that strikes suddenly on a clear day.</dd><br>
<dd>2. a bolt from the blue; bombshell</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 예고 없이 닥친 좋지 않은 일.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) An unfortunate event that occurs unexpectedly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. scolding harshly; rebuking severely</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 심한 꾸중.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A harsh scolding.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>